channel.description:
how to make a query with `actions.source.fetch()`

I'm searching about something like

    $args = [
        'post_type'             => 'post',
        'posts_per_page'        => 3,
        'orderby'               => 'date',
        'order'                 => 'DESC',
    ];

    $query = new \WP_Query( $args );
